data.description: Welcome to 8460 Spicewood Springs Rd. Nestled in the highly sought out "Preserve" neighborhood in China Spring. True property specs are 6 bedrooms, 6.5 bathrooms, two properties on one lot totaling 6594 sq feet total, a true $242.49 / sq feet including the primary home and secondary property which was completed in 2023. This breathtaking property offers a main house living space of 4992 sq feet spread across four large bedroom, four full baths, a formal dining area, home office and an upstairs isolated home theater. Additionally, this property offers an entertainers delight with a lovely stone fireplace, built-in grill, oversized covered patio, and a refreshing underground pool and attached spa. The secondary home boasts two large bedrooms, two full baths, a half bath on the exterior conveniently located for guests when enjoying the pool, a life size kitchen / dining area spread across over 1600 sq feet. In addition to a garage that could fit almost any collector's collection of fine vehicles. Words can't describe this magnificent property enough, it's a MUST SEE in person schedule your private tour today!
